.%20Instead%2C%20China%20should%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-stimulus-stock-market-consumer-deflation-outlook-real-estate-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espend%20more%20on%20its%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNet%20supply%20of%20government%20bonds%20went%20up%20significantly%20in%20August%20to%20CNY1.85tn%2C%20driven%20by%20larger%20issuances%20from%20both%20the%20central%20and%20local%20governments%2C%26quot%3B%20Bank%20of%20America%20wrote%20in%20mid-September.%20%26quot%3BUntil%20we%20see%20a%20meaningful%20step-up%20in%20fiscal%20stimulus%20to%20stabilize%20consumption%20and%20the%20property%20market%2C%20the%20downward%20trend%20of%20rates%20is%20unlikely%20to%20reverse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupportive%20measures%20could%20either%20include%20an%20upward%20revision%20to%20China's%20fiscal%20deficit%20target%20or%20the%20issuance%20of%20special%20refinancing%20bonds%20by%20local%20governments%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-bond-traders-economy-outlook-fiscal-consumer-stimulus-property-crisis-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727702720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fa920875c877a99b61a4b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fchinas-bond-traders-economy-outlook-fiscal-consumer-stimulus-property-crisis-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yields%20on%20Chinese%20government%20debt%20are%20hovering%20near%20multi-decade%20lows%20as%20investors%20remain%20unconvinced%20by%20stimulus%20efforts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fchinas-bond-traders-economy-outlook-fiscal-consumer-stimulus-property-crisis-2024-9%22%2C