st%20Netflix's%20'Baby%20Reindeer'%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFiona%20Harvey%2C%20who%20claims%20%26quot%3BMartha%26quot%3B%20is%20based%20on%20her%2C%20is%20suing%20for%20defamation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20judge%20says%20Netflix%20used%20untrue%20details%2C%20and%20should%20have%20known%20viewers%20would%20identify%20Harvey.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20judge%20has%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20was%20wrongly%20labeled%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20opening%20the%20way%20for%20a%20defamation%20lawsuit%20from%20the%20real-life%20%26quot%3BMartha%26quot%3B%20portrayed%20in%20the%20show%20to%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20Fiona%20Harvey%2C%20says%20that%20the%20hit%20Netflix%20show%20intentionally%20caused%20her%20emotional%20distress%20by%20falsely%20depicting%20her%20in%20several%20ways%20%E2%80%94%20including%20that%20she%20sexually%20assaulted%20and%20gouged%20the%20eyes%20of%20Richard%20Gadd%2C%20the%20show's%20creator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20massive%20hit%20for%20Netflix%20%E2%80%94%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-timeline-fiona-harvey-richard-gadd-piers-morgan-martha-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20released%20in%20April%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGadd%20says%20it's%20based%20on%20his%20real-life%20experiences%20of%20being%20stalked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20show%2C%20Gadd%20plays%20a%20character%20named%20Donny%20Dunn%20who%20is%20based%20on%20himself%20and%20who%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-explained-martha-scott-real-stalker-true-story-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estalked%20by%20a%20woman%20named%20Martha%20Scott%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20show%20gathered%20steam%2C%20viewers%20began%20to%20piece%20together%20who%20the%20real%20Martha%20might%20be%2C%20matching%20details%20from%20the%20show%20with%20real-life%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Gunning%20as%20Martha%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20and%20Fiona%20Harvey%20on%20%26quot%3BPiers%20Morgan%20Uncensored.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6662daedcc442a2f676ef8f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Gunning%20as%20Martha%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20and%20Fiona%20Harvey%20on%20%26quot%3BPiers%20Morgan%20Uncensored.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%2FPiers%20Morgan%2FUncensored%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Harvey%20has%20come%20forward%20and%2C%20in%20June%2C%20launched%20a%20%24170%20million%20defamation%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20streamer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20dismiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Friday%2C%20Judge%20Gary%20Klausner%20denied%20the%20motion%2C%20saying%20that%20Netflix%20had%20been%20wrong%20to%20call%20the%20show%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLess%20than%20two%20minutes%20into%20the%20first%20show%2C%20the%20text%20'this%20is%20a%20true%20story'%20appears%20on%20screen%2C%26quot%3B%20Klausner's%20ruling%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBelieving%20the%20series%20to%20be%20true%2C%20viewers%20immediately%20got%20to%20work%20trying%20to%20identify%20the%20real%20Martha%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.com.%2Fuk%2Farts%2Farticle%2Fwill-the-baby-reindeer-scandal-kill-true-story-tv-9v26txpgm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Sunday%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20cited%20unnamed%20industry%20sources%20as%20saying%20Gadd%20had%20had%20reservations%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Btrue%20story%26quot%3B%20billing%2C%20but%20that%20Netflix%20went%20ahead%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20the%20article%2C%20the%20judge%20s