After%20bowling%20out%20Bangladesh%20for%20233%20runs%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Jaiswal%20showed%20attacking%20intent%20from%20ball%20one%2C%20smashing%20the%20opponent%20team's%20bowlers%20all%20across%20the%20park.%20Rohit%20and%20Jaiswal%20mostly%20dealt%20in%20fours%20and%20sixes%20as%20they%20brought%20up%20the%2050-run%20mark%20in%20just%20three%20overs.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20a%20team%20scoring%2050%20runs%20inside%20the%20first%20three%20overs%20in%20Test%20cricket%20history%20since%20data%20collection%20began%20in%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20England%20held%20the%20record%20of%20scoring%20fastest%20fifty%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20doing%20so%20in%2026%20balls.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20managed%20to%20break%20the%20record%20by%20quite%20a%20big%20margin%2C%20reaching%20the%20team%20half-century%20in%20just%2018%20balls.%20England%20had%20created%20the%20record%20against%20West%20Indies%20earlier%20this%20year%20at%20Trent%20Bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20fastest%20team%20fifty%20before%20was%20against%20England%20in%20Chennai%20back%20in%202008.%20The%20Indian%20team%20had%20reached%20the%2050-run%20mark%20in%205.2%20overs%20in%20that%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFastest%20Team%20Fifty%20In%20Test%20Cricket%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.0%20Overs%20-%20India%20vs%20BAN%2C%20Kanpur%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.2%20Overs%20-%20England%20vs%20WI%2C%20Nottingham%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.3%20Overs%20-%20England%20vs%20SA%2C%20The%20Oval%2C%201994%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.6%20Overs%20-%20England%20vs%20SL%2C%20Manchester%2C%202002%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.2%20Overs%20-%20Sri%20Lanka%20vs%20PAK%2C%20Karachi%2C%202004%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.3%20Overs%20-%20India%20vs%20ENG%2C%20Chennai%2C%202008%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.3%20Overs%20-%20India%20vs%20WI%2C%20Port%20of%20Spain%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20later%20went%20to%20smash%20the%20world%20record%20of%20fastest%20team%20hundred%20in%20Test%20cricket%20as%20well%2C%20reaching%20the%20triple-digit%20score%20in%20just%2061%20balls%20(10.1%20overs)%2C%20beating%20their%20own%20record.%20India%20had%20earlier%20scored%20a%20team%20century%20against%20West%20Indies%20in%2012.2%20overs%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFastest%20Team%20Hundreds%20In%20Test%20History%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.1%20Overs%20-%20Ind%20vs%20Ban%20Kanpur%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12.2%20Overs%20-%20Ind%20vs%20WI%20Port%20of%20Spain%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.1%20Overs%20-%20SL%20vs%20Ban%20Colombo%20SSC%202001%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.4%20Overs%20-%20Ban%20vs%20WI%20Mirpur%202012%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.4%20Overs%20-%20Eng%20vs%20Pak%20Karachi%202022%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.4%20Overs%20-%20Eng%20vs%20Pak%20Rawalpindi%202022%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.6%20Overs%20-%20Aus%20vs%20Ind%20Perth%202012%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20game%2C%20Team%20India%20also%20smashed%20the%20record%20of%20scoring%20the%20fastest%20150%20in%20Test%20cricket%20history%2C%20doing%20so%20in%2018.2%20overs.%20India%20bettered%20their%20own%20record%20in%20the%20process%2C%20surpassing%20the%20previous%20best%20of%20reaching%20the%20150-run%20mark%20in%2021.1%20overs.%20India%20had%20done%20so%20against%20West%20Indies%20in%20Port%20of%20Spain%20in%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20Test%20cricket%2C%20the%20traditional%20format%20of%20the%20game%2C%20the%20England%20cricket%20team's%20recent%20attacking%20exploits%20earned%20their%20style%20of%20play%20the%20nickname%20of%20'Bazball'.%20However%2C%20with%20their%20performance%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20first%20three%20overs%2C%20Team%20India%20proved%20that%20they%20can%20bat%20in%20any%20gear%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20situation%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20India%20bowled%20out%20Bangladesh%20for%20233%20in%20their%20first%20innings%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20the%20second