0lose%20his%20job.%20He%20wrote%20that%20his%20seniors%20repeatedly%20humiliated%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20tense%20about%20the%20future.%20I%20have%20lost%20my%20ability%20to%20think.%20I%20am%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarun%20has%20said%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20were%20made%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20EMIs%20they%20could%20not%20recover%20from%20their%20area.%20He%20wrote%20that%20he%20had%20repeatedly%20raised%20the%20problems%20faced%20in%20recovery%20with%20his%20seniors%2C%20but%20they%20were%20not%20ready%20to%20listen%20to%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20slept%20for%2045%20days.%20I%20have%20hardly%20eaten.%20I%20am%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20stress.%20Senior%20managers%20are%20pressuring%20me%20to%20meet%20targets%20at%20any%20cost%20or%20quit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarun%20also%20wrote%20that%20he%20had%20paid%20his%20children's%20school%20fees%20till%20year-end%20and%20apologised%20to%20his%20family%20members.%20%26quot%3BYou%20all%20take%20care%20of%20Megha%2C%20Yatharth%20and%20Pihu.%20Mummy%2C%20Papa%2C%20I%20have%20never%20asked%20for%20anything%2C%20but%20am%20doing%20so%20now.%20Please%20get%20the%20second%20floor%20built%20so%20that%20my%20family%20can%20stay%20comfortably%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20his%20children%20to%20study%20well%20and%20take%20care%20of%20their%20mother.%20He%20asked%20his%20relatives%20to%20ensure%20his%20family%20gets%20the%20insurance%20money.%20He%20also%20named%20his%20seniors%20and%20asked%20his%20family%20to%20register%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20them.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20responsible%20for%20my%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarun's%20cousin%20Gaurav%20Saxena%2C%20who%20lives%20nearby%2C%20said%20he%20was%20being%20pressured%20to%20increase%20the%20recovery%20of%20loans.%20%26quot%3BAt%20a%20video%20conference%20at%206%20am%20today%2C%20his%20seniors%20built%20the%20mental%20pressure.%20They%20said%20he%20cannot%20work%20and%20he%20must%20be%20sacked.%20He%20has%20named%20them%20in%20his%20suicide%20note.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Gautam%20said%20they%20are%20getting%20the%20post-mortem%20note.%20%26quot%3BThe%20suicide%20note%20says%20his%20seniors%20were%20pressuring%20him%20over%20the%20targets.%20If%20we%20get%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20family%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarun%20Saxena's%20death%20by%20suicide%20and%20his%20letter%20blaming%20his%20senior%20managers%20come%20amid%20a%20nationwide%20conversation%20over%20toxic%20work%20culture%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20death%20of%20a%2026-year-old%20chartered%20accountant%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20letter%20by%20Anna's%20mother%20Anita%20Augustine%20sparked%20massive%20outrage%20on%20social%20media.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20chairman%20Rajiv%20Memani%2C%20she%20wrote%20that%20her%20daughter%20died%20just%20four%20months%20after%20joining%20the%20company%20and%20called%20on%20its%20leadership%20to%20change%20a%20work%20culture%20that%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20glorify%20overwork%20while%20neglecting%20the%20very%20human%20being%20behind%20the%20role%26quot%3B.%20She%20wrote%20that%20Anna%20worked%20late%20into%20the%20night%2C%20even%20on%20weekends%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20no%20opportunity%20to%20catch%20her%20breath%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Memani%20responded%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20saddened%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20as%20a%20father%2C%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20Ms%20Augustine's%20grief.%20I%20have%20conveyed%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20family%2C%20although%20nothing%20can%20fill%20the%20void%20in%20their%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EY%20India%20Chairman%20said%20he%20was%20aware%20that%20people%20had%20commented%20on%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20work%20practices%20on