%20of%20QTS%2C%20a%20data%20center%20REIT%2C%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20QTS%2C%20Blackstone%20is%20taking%20a%20proactive%20approach%20to%20the%20talent%20problem%2C%20adding%20to%20initiatives%20that%20started%20under%20the%20firm's%20previous%20owners.%20It's%20launched%20an%20internal%20Data%20Center%20Academy%20to%20find%20and%20train%20candidates%20to%20fill%20the%20specialized%20technical%20positions%20that%20can%20be%20tricky%20to%20hire%20for.%20QTS's%20talent%20programs%20have%20led%20to%20100%20new%2C%20trained%20hires%2C%20or%208%25%20of%20the%20company's%20total%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone's%20initiatives%20at%20QTS%20are%20part%20of%20the%20firm's%20talent-developing%20Career%20Pathways%20program%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20Blackstone's%20global%20head%20of%20private%20equity%2C%20Joe%20Baratta%2C%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20firm's%202024%20Career%20Pathways%20Summit%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Marcus%20Felder%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20in%20portfolio%20operations%20and%20the%20head%20of%20Career%20Pathways%2C%20said%20the%20program%20has%20two%20main%20aims%3A%20%26quot%3Bconstructively%20disrupting%20hiring%26quot%3B%20within%20its%20portfolio%20companies%20and%20creating%20programs%20and%20practices%20to%20help%20those%20new%20workers%20develop%20and%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Career%20Pathways%20seeks%20to%20help%20Blackstone's%20portfolio%20companies%20solve%20their%20talent%20problems%20by%20looking%20for%20solutions%20in%20places%20they%20may%20not%20have%20been%20looking%20before%20and%20then%20creating%20internal%20programs%20to%20develop%20that%20talent.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20September%2016%20event%20at%20Blackstone's%20Manhattan%20headquarters%2C%20Felder%20noted%20that%20portfolio%20companies%20participating%20in%20the%20program%20have%20hired%20more%20than%2010%2C500%20individuals%20from%20underrepresented%20groups.%20But%20it's%20not%20a%20charity.%20It's%20a%20business%20strategy%20to%20solve%20an%20economic%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20put%20it%20inside%20of%20our%20portfolio%20operations%20side%20of%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Blackstone's%20president%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%20Jon%20Gray%20said%20at%20the%20summit.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20charitable%20effort.%20It's%20designed%20to%20drive%20talent%20to%20companies.%26quot%3B'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20private-equity%20firms%20have%20been%20increasingly%20turning%20to%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportfolio-operations-jobs-rising-stars-of-private-equity-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eportfolio%20operations%20teams%20to%20drive%20a%20return%20on%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20high%20interest%20rates%20and%20other%20factors%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20make%20money%20from%20financial%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20Blackstone's%20Career%20Pathways%20program%20is%20helping%20the%20firm%20solve%20its%20data%20center%20talent%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20a%20QTS%20Data%20Center%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f712d7f9f6733e4be082f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20a%20QTS%20Data%20Center%3Cp%3EBlackstone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22129fcf71-74d2-45b7-93a4-667a50b5c50e%5C%22%3EInvesting%20in%20talent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQTS's%20engagement%20with%20Career%20Pathways%20began%20in%202023%20with%20an%20internal%20assessment%20of%20the%20maturity%20of%20the%20organization's%20talent%20and%20workforce%20operations%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20in%20Blackstone's%20words%2C%20a%20flash%20diagnostic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20outcomes%20of%20the%20diagnostic%20allow%20companies%20to%20take%20a%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20their%20programs%2C%20policies%2C%20and%20procedures%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20might%20start%20or%20continue%20to%20advance%20their%20objectives%20of%20hiring%2C%20retaining%2C%20and%20advancing%20untapped%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Blackstone%20spokesperson%20wrote%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20QTS%20had%20already%20been%20focusing%20on%20the%20talent%20shortage%2C%20offering%20internships%20through%20Year%20Up%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20places%20young%20adults%20without%20college%20degrees%20in%20a%20yearlong%2C%20professional%20internship%2C%20and%20SkillBridge%2C%20a%20Department%20of%20Defense%20program%20to%20help%20find%20internships%20for%20service%20members%20who%20are%20about%20to%20leave%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Blackstone's%20diagnostic%20found%20that%20the%20company%20still%20needed%20to%20find%20and%20train%20more%20candidates%20who%20could%20fill%20the%20specialized%20technical%20positions%20required%20for%20a%20data%20center.%20So%20it%20created%20its%20own%20internal%20program%20called%20the%20Data%20Center%20Academy%2C%20which%20helps%20train%20workers%20on%20the%20skills%20necessary%20for%20the%20growing%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruitment%20efforts%20have%20focused%20on%20critical%20operations%20employees%20who%20work%20within%20data%20centers%20and%20monitor%20and%20manage%20the%20facilities'%20infrastructure%2C%20hardware%2C%20and%20various%20technologies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20more%20general%20corporate%20services%20roles%20that%20range%20from%20finance%20to%20customer%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20firm%20has%20placed%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efive%20Data%20Center%20Academy%20cohorts%20in%20eleven%20markets.%20Cohorts%20include%20seven%20or%20eight%20employees%20whose%20members%20are%20offered%20direct%20career%20mentorship%20from%20senior%20employees%20within%20the%20company.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EQTS%20also%20has%20a%20growing%20leadership%20development%20for%20promising%20employees%20with%20bachelor's%20degrees%20and%20four%20or%20more%20years%20of%20work%20experience.%20The%20program%20gives%20employees%20nine%20to%20eighteen%20months%20to%20try%20other%20roles%20in%20the%20business%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20new%20job%20once%20they've%20found%20their%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoffers%20more%20traditional%20student-focused%20summer%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202021%2C%20the%20company's%20new%20talent%20sources%20have%20yielded%20100%20hires%20that%20are%20new%20to%20the%20industry%2C%20making%20up%208%25%20of%20QTS's%20employee%20base.%20Of%20the%20employees%20that%20have%20gone%20through%20QTS's%20apprenticeships%2C%2073%25%20were%20converted%20to%20full%20time%20roles%2C%20and%2015%25%20of%20them%20were%20promoted%20in%20their%20first%20year%20of%20full-time%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETracking%20data%2C%20such%20as%20the%20number%20of%20apprenticeships%20converted%20to%20hires%2C%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20program%20because%20it%20helps%20the%20firm%20calculate%20its%20ROI%20and%20justify%20these%20programs'%20contributions%20to%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20all%20contributions%20are%20so%20easy%20to%20quantify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22590%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kimberly%20Hines%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20suit%2C%20stands%20at%20a%20podium%20in%20front%20of%20a%20large%20screen%20with%20the%20contents%20blurred.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f716fbde59ade1a3b5815a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKimberly%20Hines%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20experience%20and%20belonging%20at%20QTS%2C%20speaks%20at%20the%20Career%20Pathways%20event.%20Note%3A%20the%20photo%20has%20been%20edited%20to%20blur%20the%20contents%20of%20her%20presentation.%3Cp%3EBlackstone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20thing%20I%20would%20say%20about%20the%20employees%20who%20have%20joined%20us%20is%20that%20they%20are%20bringing%20new%20perspectives%20and%20skills%2C%20they're%20launching%20new%20programs%2C%20they're%20engaging%20in%20innumerable%20ways%20and%20just%20being%20a%20great%20value%20to%20our%20company's%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Kimberly%20Hines%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20belonging%20and%20experience%20at%20QTS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221028c84-4c90-4b65-aca5-445121d8de6f%5C%22%3EA%20new%20path%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlhaji%20Dawon%20first%20heard%20about%20Year%20Up%20while%20at%20a%20soccer%20game%20with%20a%20friend.%20Their%20team%20was%20losing%2C%20so%20they%20started%20talking%20about%20careers.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Dawon%20was%20working%20for%20a%20manufacturing%20company%20in%20a%20warehouse%2C%20making%20little%20over%20minimum%20wage.%20He%20was%20planning%20to%20eventually%20attend%20college%20for%20cybersecurity%2C%20but%20he%20hadn't%20started%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDawon's%20friend%20had%20recently%20completed%20the%20Year%20Up%20program%20and%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it%2C%20had%20landed%20an%20impressive%20job.%20Dawon%20was%20convinced%20to%20apply%20to%20the%20program.%20He%20was%20accepted%20and%20then%20placed%20at%20QTS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227039%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Five%20people%20sitting%20at%20a%20couch%20on%20stage%20with%20a%20large%20television%20screen%20behind%20them%20and%20people%20sitting%20in%20the%20foreground.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f7171175c877a99b617d1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225279%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlhaji%20Dawon%2C%20center%2C%20speaking%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20at%20the%20Blackstone%20Career%20Pathways%20Summit.%3Cp%3EBlackstone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20internship%2C%20he%20was%20hired%20full-time%20into%20a%20critical%20operations%20role.%20Despite%20not%20yet%20having%20gotten%20that%20degree%20in%20cybersecurity%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20work%20and%20excel%20alongside%20