20rounds%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20Commission%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20and%20Madras%20High%20Courts.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20when%20nothing%20worked%2C%20he%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20allow%20such%20a%20young%20talented%20boy%20to%20go%20away.%20He%20cannot%20be%20left%20in%20lurch.%20He%20went%20to%20Jharkhand%20Legal%20Services%20Authority.%20Then%20to%20Chennai%20Legal%20Services%20Authority%20and%20then%20he%20is%20sent%20to%20High%20Court.%20He%20is%20a%20Dalit%20boy%20being%20made%20to%20run%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20ordering%20the%20IIT%20to%20admit%20the%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20a%20talented%20student%20like%20the%20petitioner%20who%20belongs%20to%20a%20marginalised%20group%20who%20did%20all%20to%20secure%20admission%20should%20not%20be%20left%20out...%20we%20direct%20that%20candidate%20is%20granted%20admission%20to%20IIT%20Dhanbad%20and%20let%20him%20be%20in%20the%20same%20batch%20to%20which%20he%20would%20have%20been%20granted%20admission%20if%20the%20fees%20would%20have%20been%20paid%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner's%20counsel%20said%20the%20student's%20father%20earns%20Rs%20450%20daily.%20%26quot%3BThe%20task%20of%20arranging%2017%2C500%20is%20a%20big%20deal.%20He%20collected%20money%20from%20villagers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20that%20stopped%20him%20from%20paying%20was%20the%20inability%20to%20pay%20and%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20we%20need%20to%20see%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20used%20its%20extraordinary%20powers%20under%20Article%20142%20of%20the%20Constitution%20in%20asking%20the%20IIT%20Dhanbad%20to%20admit%20Atul%20Kumar%20into%20its%20Electrical%20Engineering%20BTech%20course.%C2%A0Article%20142%20of%20the%20Constitution%20empowers%20the%20top%20court%20to%20pass%20any%20order%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20best.%20%3Cem%3EAchha%20kariye%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Do%20well)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20told%20the%2018-year-old%20student%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20village%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20district%20of%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20relieved%20Atul%20said%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-train-back-on-track-dalit-student-after-top-court-asks-iit-to-admit-him-6684065%5C%22%3Ederailed%20train%20is%20back%20on%20track%20now%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20the%20seat.%20I%20am%20very%20happy.%20The%20court%20said%20my%20seat%20could%20not%20be%20snatched%20away%20solely%20due%20to%20a%20financial%20problem.%20The%20train%20that%20had%20derailed%20is%20back%20on%20track%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20with%20a%20smile.%20Atul%20said%20he%20was%20hopeful%20of%20getting%20help%20from%20the%20top%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20lies%20ahead%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20work%20hard%20and%20become%20an%20electrical%20engineer%20from%20IIT-Dhanbad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Parents%20Went%20Through%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20Atul%20Kumar%20failed%20to%20deposit%20Rs%2017%2C500%20as%20the%20acceptance%20fee%20by%205%20pm%20on%20June%2024%2C%20the%20deadline%20for%20depositing%20the%20fee%20for%20blocking%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student's%20father%20managed%20to%20crowdsource%20the%20amount%20by%204%3A45%20pm%20on%20the%20last%20day.%20As%20Atul%20began%20uploading%20his%20documents%2C%20the%20time%20for%20submission%20of%20fee%20was%20up.%20A%20dream%20crushed%2C%20the%20family%20regrouped%20and%20took%20the%20legal%20route.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20student%20wrote%20the%20exam%20at%20a%20centre%20in%20Jha