ent%20to%20kindergarten%20without%20knowing%20English%2C%20so%20I%20took%20language%20classes%20to%20catch%20up.%20In%20our%20household%2C%20I%20was%20always%20reading%20the%20bills%20and%20letters.%20I%20also%20took%20care%20of%20my%20three%20little%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20didn't%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fcan-you-change-social-security-number%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESocial%20Security%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20credit%20lines%2C%20so%20they%20always%20paid%20in%20cash.%20Eventually%2C%20they%20did%20get%20driver's%20licenses%2C%20but%20they%20were%20always%20fearful%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20renew%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20weren't%20able%20to%20travel%20back%20to%20Mexico%20when%20some%20of%20our%20family%20members%20died.%20For%20a%20long%20time%2C%20we%20didn't%20even%20go%20on%20trips%20out%20of%20Nashville%20because%20of%20fear%20of%20the%20law.%20We%20were%20always%20looking%20over%20our%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20my%20parents%20have%20hustled%20to%20live%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-dream-immigrants-made-a-fortune-in-the-us-2014-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284fbc695-974b-4b9c-9294-b69df27bac1a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20nurse%20but%20struggled%20to%20get%20into%20college%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20grew%20up%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20family%2C%20I%20always%20had%20a%20nurturing%20attitude%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-neurosurgeon-mom-demanding-job-parenting-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20in%20medicine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20a%20Social%20Security%20number%20meaning%20I%20couldn't%20apply%20for%20government%20assistance.%20My%20parents%20told%20me%