everything%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20it%20was%20jarring%20and%20very%20unexpected%20to%20see%20myself%20on%20someone's%20Instagram%20without%20a%20hijab.%20This%20class%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20women-only%20space%2C%20and%20I%20had%20dressed%20accordingly.%20But%20now%20I%20felt%20uncomfortable%20at%20the%20thought%20of%20not%20only%20being%20filmed%20without%20knowing%20but%20also%20having%20that%20video%20posted%20on%20a%20public%20platform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b8c9da6-809e-44cf-9831-d8cdb9234409%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20asked%20people%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20what%20they%20post%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20only%20have%20been%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20but%20it%20was%20enough%20for%20me%20to%20see%20myself%20clearly%2C%20which%20meant%20other%20viewers%20would%2C%20too.%20When%20I%20messaged%20my%20trainer%20asking%20her%20to%20take%20it%20down%2C%20she%20did%2C%20thankfully.%20But%20her%20response%2C%20trying%20to%20justify%20it%20and%20make%20it%20seem%20like%20her%20posting%20wasn't%20that%20big%20a%20deal%2C%20made%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20she%20didn't%20take%20my%20concern%20too%20seriously.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20this%20has%20happened%20to%20me.%20It's%20not%20even%20the%20first%20time%20this%20has%20happened%20to%20me%20in%20a%20gym%20class%2C%20despite%20my%20multiple%20reminders%20not%20to%20take%20pictures%20or%20videos%20of%20me%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbilqis-abdul-qaadir-hijab-muslim-basketball-iran-protest-mahsa-amini-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithout%20a%20hijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20both%20my%20instructors%20and%20people%20around%20me%20every%20time%20I'm%20in%20a%20women-only%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20had%20friends%20accidentally%20post%20Snapchats%20of%20a%20group%20gathering.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20for%20a%20friend's%20pre-wedding%20event%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20celebrate%20with%20a%20relaxing%20girl-only%20pool%20day.%20It%20wasn't%20relaxing%20for%20me%3B%20I%20spent%20half%20the%20event%20either%20taking%20group%20pictures%20for%20everyone%20else%20or%20sitting%20in%20a%20corner%20to%20avoid%20being%20in%20everyone's%20videos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20I%20have%20asked%20people%20to%20be%20careful%20to%20make%20sure%20I'm%20not%20in%20any%20pictures%2C%20I've%20become%20increasingly%20uncomfortable%20at%20these%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-australian-visited-japan-women-only-train-segregation-disrespectful-harassment-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewomen-only%20gatherings%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I've%20felt%20like%20I'm%20asking%20for%20too%20much.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20know%20that%20none%20of%20this%20is%20done%20maliciously%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20hold%20anyone%20at%20fault.%20Most%20often%20my%20request%20probably%20slipped%20the%20other%20person's%20mind.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220cf831a9-c27b-4358-a9a2-5390b2181e92%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20way%20we%20post%20on%20social%20media%20has%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20an%20outsider%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsking%20someone%20not%20to%20post%20on%20social%20media%20can%20be%20awkward.%20And%20while%20this%20is%20no%20one's%20fault%2C%20it%20has%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20an%20outsider%2C%20even%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20my%20own%20country%2C%20and%20my%20community.%20More%20than%20that%2C%20it%20means%20my%20relationship%20with%20my%20hijab%20has%20also%20slowly%20changed%20over%20the%20years%2C%20as%20there%20are%20fewer%20spaces%20where%20I%20feel%20comfortable%20being%20without%20it%20outside%20of%20the%20comfort%20of%20my%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20attended%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20hr