0people%20online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727691663000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113814560%2Cimgsize-1296916.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fhow-hackers-are-using-apple-and-microsoft-to-scam-people-online%2Farticleshow%2F113814278.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hackers%20are%20exploiting%20the%20names%20of%20trusted%20companies%20like%20Apple%20and%20Microsoft%20to%20defraud%20users%2C%20especially%20following%20new%20product%20launches.%20Using%20AI%20technology%2C%20these%20scams%20become%20harder%20to%20detect%20through%20deceptive%20pop-up%20messages%20and%20malvertising.%20Victims%20should%20change%20their%20passwords%20immediately%20and%20notify%20banks%20and%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20about%20the%20scam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fhow-hackers-are-using-apple-and-microsoft-to-scam-people-online%2Farticleshow%2F113814278.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20New%20Delhi's%20Air%20Quality%20Can%20Choke%20Its%20Geopolitical%20Influence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fnsr189eg_pollution_625x300_30_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20ongoing%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20has%20decried%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20for%20not%20serving%20its%20purpose.%20The%20Commission%20was%20set%20up%20in%202021%20through%20an%20ordinance%20after%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20in%20National%20Capital%20Region%20and%20Adjoining%20Areas%20Act%202021%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%2030%2C%202021.%20What%20the%20apex%20court%20has%20observed%20is%20that%20three%20years%2C%20millions%20of%20dollars%2C%20and%20several%20opportunities%20have%20gone%20down%20the%20drain%20while%20India's%20capital%2C%20yet%20again%2C%20prepares%20to%20choke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20of%20New%20Delhi%2C%20policymakers%20and%20plebeians%20alike%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20eased%20into%20the%20city's%20toxicity%3A%20polluters%20continue%20to%20pollute%20without%20any%20fear%20of%20penalty%20or%20punishment%2C%20and%20the%20wealthy%20find%20ways%20to%20avoid%20being%20in%20the%20city%20during%20the%20choke%20months%20-%20November%20to%20February.%20The%20world%2C%20however%2C%20is%20watching%20the%20poison%20in%20Delhi's%20air%20with%20a%20bated%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Hardship%20Allowance'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20New%20Delhi%20was%20adjudged%20to%20be%20the%20most%20polluted%20capital%20city%20in%20the%20world%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sixth%20Annual%20World%20Air%20Quality%20Report.%20The%20city's%20air%20has%20PM2.5%20concentrations%20that%20are%20more%20than%20ten%20times%20the%20WHO%20annual%20guideline.%20This%20factoid%20on%20paper%20reads%20straight%20out%20of%20a%20dystopian%20work.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20categorises%20New%20Delhi%20as%20a%20city%20that%20merits%20a%20%26quot%3BPost%20(Hardship)%20Differential%26quot%3B%20allowance.%20The%20hardship%20allowance%20for%20being%20posted%20to%20India's%20capital%20is%20pegged%20at%2025%25%20of%20basic%20compensation%20-%20the%20same%20as%20the%20bombed-out%20Beirut%20or%20the%20regional%20posts%20in%20Antarctica%20or%20the%20Arctic%20Circle.%20In%201997%2C%20this%20allowance%20used%20to%20be%2010%25.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20means%20on%20an%20everyday%20basis%20is%20even%20more%20disturbing.%20Despite%20a%20substantially%20heftier%20pay%20packet%2C%20diplomats%20are%20hesitant.%20Delhi%20is%20scary.%20It%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20most%20embassies%20and%20high%20commissions%20begin%20to%20show%20signs%20of%20thinning%20personnel%20strength%20post-autumn%20every%20year.%20The%20'holiday'%20season%20starts%20early%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20of%20reacting%20to%20this%20phenomenon%3A%20brushing%20it%20off%20as%20typical%20Global%20North%20snobbery%20or%20assessing%20the%20implications%20of%20being%20treated%20at%20par%20with%20a%20war%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPassing%20The%20Buck%2C%20Every%20Year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi's%20inability%20to%20control%20pollution%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20country's%20democratic%20governance.%20It%20is%2C%20after%20all%2C%20commonsensical%20to%20ask%20how%20robust%20the%20mechanisms%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%20are%20when%20they%20cannot%20ensure%20even%20clean%20air%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20region.%20What%20the%20world%20witnesses%20is%20a%20perpetual%20passing-the-buck%20game%20every%20year%20while%20hazardous%20conditions%20continue%20to%20jeopardise%20people's%20health%20and%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20biggest%20calling%20card%20in%20the%20global%20arena%20is%20its%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20democracy.%20This%20is%20what%20sets%20New%20Delhi%20apart%20from%20other%20capitals%20like%20Beijing%20or%20Abu%20Dhabi%20in%20terms%20of%20promise.%20The%20failure%20to%20check%20the%20pollution%20hazard%20becomes%20a%20stick%20with%20which%20to%20beat%20India's%20democracy.%20Can%20we%20afford%20this%20undermining%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20take%20the%20geopolitics%20aspect%20of%20environmental%20deterioration%20a%20little%20further.%20In%202010%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20region%20saw%20a%20sharp%20decline%20in%20air%20pollution%20levels%2C%20becoming%20an%20outlier.%20Reduced%20economic%20activity%20due%20to%20sanctions%20and%20conflicts%20was%20cited%20as%20the%20primary%20driver%20for%20this%20phenomenon.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20UN-backed%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%20led%20to%20lower%20emissions%20from%20oil%20tankers%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf.%20Strife%20in%20Syria%20precluded%20any%20industrial%20growth%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20significant%20improvement%20in%20the%20air%20quality.%20How%20long%20before%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20powerful%20get%20certain%20ideas%20on%20tackling%20environmental%20deterioration%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Can't%20Just%20Wish%20Away%20The%20Problem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20promoting%20itself%20as%20a%20powerful%20player%20in%20the%20global%20security%20gambit.%20It%20seems%20to%20be%20getting%20almost%20too%20sure%20of%20its%20importance.%20However%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20environmental%20policy%2C%20European%20and%20North%20American%20countries%20might%20want%20to%20weather%20the%20geopolitical%20risks.%20A%202023%20study%20published%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Environmental%20Management%3C%2Fem%3E%20indicates%20that%20while%20%26quot%3Bgeopolitical%20risks%20significantly%20influence%20environmental%20policy%26quot%3B%20in%20many%20EU%20member%20states%2C%20%26quot%3Benvironmental%20policy%20causes%20geopolitical%20risks%20only%20in%20Latvia%26quot%3B.%20The%20message%20is%20clear.%20Perceived%20geopolitical%20risks%20are%20unlikely%20to%20undermine%20environmental%20policies.%20Is%20India%20certain%20of%20cushioning%20itself%20against%20this%20altered%20approach%20that%20renders%20it%20not%20so%20important%20anymore%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20India%20is%20being%20decried%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20significant%20polluters.%20Our%20prickliness%20and%20denunciation%20of%20such%20proclamations%20cannot%20mitigate%20their%20reputational%20damage.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20further%20complications%20to%20New%20Delhi's%20air%20issue.%20While%20we%20are%20somewhat%20fortunate%20to%20have%20even%20more%20polluted%20neighbours%20-%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan%20-%20a%20diplomatic%20event%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20become%20territorial%20and%20military%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%20Recently%2C%20the%20South%20Korean%20government%20monitored%20and%20quantified%20the%20influence%20of%20border-crossing%20particulate%20matter%20from%20China.%20This%20is%20literally%20taking%20the%20fight%20to%20atmospheric%20levels.%20Pakistan%2C%20along%20similar%20lines%2C%20blames%20the%20farm%20fires%20of%20Punjab%20(and%20Haryana)%20directly%20impacting%20Lahore's%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20can%20continue%20to%20sit%20and%20watch%20the%20many%20fires%20in%20its%20backyard%20without%20changing%20the%20status%20quo.%20However%2C%20it%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20the%20consequences%20such%20a%20signalling%20may%20entail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727691660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F0tmbu1qo_pollution_625x300_30_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnew-delhis-air-quality-may-choke-its-geopolitical-influence-6683436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Already%2C%20India%20is%20being%20decried%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20significant%20polluters.%20Our%20prickliness%20and%20denunciation%20of%20such%20proclamations%20cannot%20mitigate%20their%20reputational%20damage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnew-delhis-air-quality-may-choke-its-geopolitical-influence-6683436%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Period%20Crime%20Drama%20%E2%80%9CVon%20Fock%E2%80%9D%20Toplines%20Zolba%20Productions%E2%80%99%20International%