will%20come%20to%20power.%20The%20Mughals%20ruled%20for%20850%20years%2C%20they%20could%20not...%20those%20who%20are%20burning%20the%20country%20must%20note%20that%20the%20people%20have%20woken%20up.%20They%20gave%20a%20reply%20in%20Parliament%20(polls).%20And%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20in%202027%2C%20you%20will%20surely%20go%20and%20we%20will%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20a%20video.%C2%A0The%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20due%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20legislator's%20remarks%20have%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubrat%20Pathak%2C%20former%20MP%20and%20BJP%20general%20secretary%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20said%20the%20MLA's%20remarks%20raise%20questions%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20must%20answer.%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20why%20(Samajwadi%20Party%20chief)%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20busy%20dividing%20Hindus%3F%20So%20that%20a%20particular%20community's%20wish%20is%20fulfilled%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20said%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20must%20remember%20that%20the%20country%20had%20changed.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hindus%20have%20made%20Narendra%20Modi%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20time%20and%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20two%20terms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Sunil%20Sajan%20said%20the%20party%20does%20not%20agree%20with%20Mehboob%20Ali's%20remark%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20defeated%20because%20the%20Muslim%20population%20has%20increased.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20is%20true%20that%20inflation%20has%20increased%2C%20unemployment%20has%20increased%2C%20BJP's%20corruption%20has%20increased%2C%20their%20lies%20have%20increased%2C%20their%20politics%20of%20hate%20has%20increased...%20the%20borders%20are%20not%20secure%2C%20states%20are%20burning%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20silent.%20So%20a%20large%20population%20wants%20to%20ensure%20the%20BJP's%20defeat.%20S