0Will%20The%20Wind%20Blow%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjirkee9o_kahsmir_625x300_24_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20final%20round%20of%20voting%20for%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20tomorrow%20(October%201).%20This%20is%20the%20first%20assembly%20poll%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20after%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%2010%20years%20have%20seen%20momentous%20changes%20in%20the%20political%20complexion%20of%20the%20region.%20Soon%20after%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20gave%20a%20special%20status%20to%20the%20state%2C%20was%20rescinded.%20Further%2C%20it%20was%20divided%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20%E2%80%93%20Ladakh%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20promised%20to%20restore%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood%20in%20future.%20And%20while%20a%20few%20regional%20players%20have%20sought%20a%20restoration%20of%20the%20special%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20non-committal%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Contest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20this%20year%20were%20preceded%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20BJP%20contested%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20and%20won%20both.%20In%20the%20remaining%20three%20seats%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20won%20two%20and%20an%20Independent%20candidate%20was%20elected%20from%20one.%20The%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20was%20unable%20to%20open%20its%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20key%20leaders%20of%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%2C%20lost%20the%20elections.%20Abdullah%20was%20defeated%20by%20an%20independent%20candidate%2C%20Engineer%20Rashid%20(who%20contested%20the%20elections%20from%20jail)%2C%20while%20Mufti%20lost%20to%20the%20NC's%20Mian%20Altaf%20Ahmed%20Larvi.%20Both%20fell%20behind%20by%20over%202%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%2090%20assembly%20segments%20are%20taken%20into%20account%20for%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%2C%20then%20the%20National%20Conference%20led%20in%2036%20assembly%20seats%20and%20its%20alliance%20partner%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20was%20ahead%20in%20seven%2C%20bringing%20their%20combined%20strength%20close%20to%20the%20half-way%20mark.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20in%2029%20segments%2C%20the%20PDP%20in%20five%2C%20and%20Independents%20and%20others%20in%20the%20remaining%2013%20seats.%20The%20NC%20and%20the%20BJP%20improved%20their%20performance%20compared%20to%20the%202014%20assembly%20polls%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20PDP%20faced%20a%20sharp%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%20Reasons%20This%20Election%20Is%20So%20Critical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20assembly%20election%20has%20evoked%20tremendous%20interest%20both%20within%20the%20country%20and%20internationally%20for%20multiple%20reasons.%20The%20verdict%20will%20reflect%20the%20popular%20mood%20after%20the%20Article%20370%20move%20and%20the%20subsequent%20developments%20in%20the%20region.%20That%20this%20is%20the%20first%20election%20in%2010%20years%20also%20means%20that%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20new%20generation%20of%20voters%20-%20those%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-28%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20voting%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20group%20represents%20an%20important%20segment%20of%20the%20electorate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20dimensions%20that%20assume%20importance%20in%20the%20current%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20election.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20voter%20turnout%2C%20which%20many%20see%20as%20a%20barometer%20to%20measure%20the%20popular%20response%20to%20the%20democratic%20process%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20first%20phase%20of%20polling%20saw%20over%2061%25%20voting%2C%20while%20the%20second%20phase%20saw%2057%25%20of%20electors%20coming%20out%20to%20vote.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20assembly%20polls%20had%20attracted%20a%2065%25%20turnout%20despite%20a%20boycott%20call.%20Thus%2C%20while%20the%20initial%20numbers%20this%20year%20may%20seem%20lower%2C%20they%20still%20represent%20a%20strong%20turnout.%20It%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20first%20two%20phases%20of%20voting%20were%20free%20of%20violence%20and%20saw%20peaceful%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounting%20is%20scheduled%20for%20October%208.%20Media%20reports%20indicate%20that%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20especially%2C%20economic%20issues%20like%20development%2C%20employment%2C%20price%20rise%2C%20and%20peace%20and%20security%20are%20key%20factors%20that%20influenced%20their%20decision.%20The%20two%20regional%20parties%2C%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%2C%20have%20focused%20on%20their%20demand%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20statehood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fate%20Of%20Old%20Players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20region%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20have%20distinctly%20different%20political%20orientations.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20had%20an%20upper%20hand%20in%20Jammu%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%20have%20been%20key%20players%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20valley.%20The%20final%20result%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20how%20much%20support%20these%20players%20have%20across%20the%20region%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leads%20one%20to%20the%20third%20and%20last%20factor%20due%20to%20which%20the%20current%20assembly%20polls%20are%20significant.%20This%20election%20has%20seen%20the%20entry%20of%20several%20new%20local%20parties%20and%20independent%20candidates%2C%20whose%20performance%20will%20be%20watched%20closely.%20Do%20national%20parties%20and%20traditional%20regional%20players%20continue%20to%20hold%20sway%2C%20or%20have%20new%20players%20tipped%20the%20scales%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20this%20would%20also%20be%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20cut%20and%20thrust%20of%20the%20overall%20politics%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dr.%20Sandeep%20Shastri%20is%20the%20National%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20Lokniti%20Network)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727680800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjirkee9o_kahsmir_625x300_24_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fj-k-election-10-years-on-which-way-will-the-wind-blow-6682102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Jammu%20region%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20have%20distinctly%20different%20political%20orientations.%20The%20final%20result%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20how%20much%20support%20these%20political%20players%20have%20across%20the%20region%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fj-k-election-10-years-on-which-way-will-the-wind-blow-6682102%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'To%20hold%20general%20election%20on%20October%2027'%3A%20Japan's%20next%20PM%20Shigeru%20Ishiba%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727680019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113807706%2Cimgsize-806975.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world