%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbeirut-like-a-horror-movie-families-return-from-lebanon-after-fleeing-israeli-bombings-13223830%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Can%20Swarathma%20%26amp%3B%20Coldplay%20Teach%20Us%20About%20Inclusivity%20for%20the%20Deaf%20Community%20in%20Music%20Events%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20last%20full%20week%20of%20September%20marks%20the%20celebration%20of%20International%20Week%20of%20the%20Deaf%2C%20providing%20a%20valuable%20opportunity%20for%20the%20Deaf%20community%20to%20unite.%20Historically%2C%20this%20community%20has%20developed%20a%20unique%20form%20of%20self-expression%2C%20asserting%20that%20their%20identity%20is%20rooted%20in%20belonging%20to%20a%20cultural%20and%20linguistic%20minority.%20This%20identity%20transcends%20boundaries%20of%20class%2C%20race%2C%20and%20gender%20and%20is%20deeply%20tied%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fi-decided-to-become-a-special-educator-and-to-help-disabled-people-communicate-in-sign-language%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efluency%20in%20sign%20language%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20encompasses%20individuals%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20hearing%20loss%2C%20their%20families%2C%20sign%20language%20interpreters%2C%20and%20others%20who%20work%20with%20sign%20language%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20linguistic%20minority%2C%20the%20community%20often%20struggles%20to%20socialise%20outside%20their%20close%20circles%2C%20making%20it%20challenging%20to%20integrate%20into%20mainstream%20culture.%20This%20difficulty%20is%20partly%20due%20to%20persistent%20barriers%20that%20limit%20their%20opportunities%20to%20connect.%20Two%20key%20factors%20contribute%20to%20this%20%E2%80%94%20lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20the%20Deaf%20community%20and%20the%20mainstream%20community%E2%80%99s%20unfamiliarity%20with%20sign%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20theme%20for%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20International%20Week%20of%20the%20Deaf%20is%20%E2%80%98Sign%20Up%20for%20Sign%20Language%20Rights.%E2%80%99%20The%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20advocating%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159928%2Fnipun-malhotra-indian-sign-language-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20recognition%20of%20sign%20language%20as%20a%20fully%20developed%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20deserving%20of%20equal%20status%20alongside%20spoken%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20this%2C%20the%20British%20rock%20band%20Coldplay%20has%20committed%20to%20providing%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20at%20their%20upcoming%20concerts%20in%20India.%20As%20part%20of%20their%20efforts%20to%20enhance%20accessibility%2C%20the%20band%20will%20offer%20local%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20at%20every%20performance%2C%20along%20with%20other%20support%20measures%20for%20Deaf%20or%20hard-of-hearing%20guests.%20This%20initiative%20is%20part%20of%20Coldplay%E2%80%99s%20broader%20commitment%20to%20inclusivity%20during%20their%20%E2%80%98Music%20of%20the%20Spheres%20World%20Tour%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20will%20stop%20in%20Mumbai%20on%2018%2C%2019%2C%20and%2021%20January%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20like%20these%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%20as%20a%20growing%20movement%20seeks%20to%20foster%20inclusion%20for%20the%20Deaf%20community.%20However%2C%20many%20advancements%20still%20remain%20limited%20in%20scope%20and%20reach.%20According%20to%20Eurostat%2C%20the%20European%20Union%E2%80%99s%20statistical%20office%2C%20there%20are%20nine%20key%20indicators%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20quality%20of%20life.%20While%20material%20living%20conditions%20and%20education%20are%20crucial%2C%20equal%20importance%20is%20placed%20on%20leisure%2C%20social%20interactions%2C%20and%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20overall%20life%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20several%20Deaf%20employees%20at%20our%20company%2C%20and%20they%20are%20among%20the%20most%20friendly%20and%20enjoyable%20colleagues%20to%20work%20with.%20However%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20that%20conversations%20beyond%20the%20immediate%20scope%20of%20work%20are%20a%20challenge%20and%20this%20impacts%20their%20long-term%20career%20progression%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mira%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20practices%20manager%20at%20a%20leading%20IT%20Firm%20in%20Gurgaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20social%20and%20cultural%20events%20are%20inaccessible%20to%20the%20Deaf%20and%20hard-of-hearing%20community%20as%20there%20are%20no%20systems%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20their%20inclusion.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20laws%20or%20policy%20directives%2C%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20community%20depends%20entirely%20on%20the%20initiative%20of%20other%20organisations.%20This%20gap%20is%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20mainstream%20often%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20an%20understanding%20of%20how%20to%20include%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20recently%20attended%20the%20Indian%20folk%20rock%20band%2C%20Swarathma%E2%80%99s%20concert%20in%20New%20Delhi%20where%20the%20lyrics%20of%20their%20songs%20were%20played%20on%20a%20screen%2C%20and%20thought%20about%20how%20it%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20include%20the%20Deaf%20and%20hard%20of%20hearing%20people%20as%20well.%20The%20very%20next%20day%2C%20I%20mentioned%20this%20to%20my%20friend%20and%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98But%20why%20would%20Deaf%20people%20attend%20a%20music%20concert%3F%E2%80%99%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20the%20layperson%20may%20not%20know%20how%20Deaf%20people%20may%20be%20experiencing%20and%20enjoying%20music%20or%20participating%20in%20cultural%20events%2C%E2%80%9D%20comments%20Raghav%2C%20a%20music%20enthusiast%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwarathma%2C%20recently%20also%20performed%20at%20a%20concert%20with%20a%20sign%20language%20interpreter%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20When%20asked%20about%20their%20experience%2C%20Jishnu%2C%20a%20band%20member%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CConcerts%20are%20not%20just%20about%20the%20music.%20If%20it%20were%20just%20about%20listening%20to%20music%2C%20you%20would%20just%20press%20play%20on%20an%20MP3%20player%20instead.%20Our%20concert%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20collective%20energy%20that%20is%20radiated%20by%20the%20performers.%20It%20is%20reflected%20onto%20the%20audience%20and%20then%20reflected%20back%20to%20the%20performers%20in%20what%20one%20hopes%20is%20a%20virtuous%20circle%20of%20ever-increasing%20energy%20that%20creates%20an%20unforgettable%20communal%20experience.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20say%20that%20persons%20with%20any%20kind%20of%20ability%20can%20or%20cannot%20or%20should%20or%20should%20not%20experience%20something%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%2C%20a%20Deaf%20trainer%20at%20v-shesh%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20events%20organised%20by%20and%20for%20the%20Deaf%20community%20are%20accessible%20to%20me.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20not%20only%20do%20I%20miss%20out%20on%20opportunities%20to%20attend%20interesting%20events%2C%20I%20also%20miss%20out%20on%20forging%20friendships%20and%20meeting%20like-minded%20people%20with%20similar%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20gathering%20for%20a%20performance%2C%20events%20like%20concerts%20or%20plays%20provide%20individuals%20with%20the%20opportunity%20to%20form%20a%20community%20and%20experience%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging.%20These%20shared%20experiences%20foster%20connection%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F245995%2Fmit-innovation-start-up-deaf-education-study-bleetech-innovations-oralism-speech-therapy-lip-reading-pune-mit-technology-div200%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreating%20a%20space%20where%20individuals%20can%20engage%20and%20feel%20included%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20Deaf%20community%20experience%20music%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20multiple%20levels%20of%20Deafness%2C%20and%20people%20across%20the%20hearing%20spectrum%20may%20experience%20and%20enjoy%20music%20in%20different%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20ways%20in%20which%20someone%20Deaf%20might%20enjoy%20music%20is%20by%20feeling%20the%20vibrations.%20The%20bass%20notes%20and%20beats%20often%20create%20vibrations%20that%20they%20may%20use%20to%20%E2%80%98listen%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20song.%20This%20also%20provides%20them%20with%20multiple%20ways%20to%20enjoy%20a%20song%20%E2%80%94%20a%20song%20felt%20through%20a%20speaker%20at%20home%20is%20very%20different%20from%20how%20one%20might%20experience%20the%20song%20at%20a%20live%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%204608px)%20100vw%2C%204608px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshutterstock_1095618458_11zon-1727440758.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Including%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20at%20cultural%20events%20will%20make%20them%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20Deaf%20community.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshutterstock_1095618458_11zon-1727440758.jpg%204608w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshutterstock_1095618458_11zon-1727440758-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshutterstock_1095618458_11zon-1727440758-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshutterstock_1095618458_11zon-1727440758-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshutterstock_1095618458_11zon-1727440758-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen