villages%20in%20other%20communities%20and%20tribes%2C%20across%20the%20region.%20The%20people%20of%20Manipur%20should%20unite%20and%20work%20together%20to%20protect%20the%20pangolin.%20As%20for%20communities%20like%20Chingjaro%2C%20protecting%20the%20pangolin%20might%20as%20well%20be%20their%20first%20step%20into%20the%20conservation%20of%20their%20local%20wildlife.%20After%20all%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20pangolins%20that%20ensure%20that%20the%20mountains%20of%20Manipur%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Madhumay%20Mallik%20%E2%80%94%20a%20conservation%20writer%2C%20photographer%2C%20and%20graphic%20designer%2C%20currently%20engaged%20with%20the%20communications%20team%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wti.org.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Madhumay%20Mallik%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727177601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367156%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20regional%20conflict%2C%20diverse%20communities%20in%20Manipur%20are%20coming%20together%2C%20recognising%20that%20protecting%20pangolins%20is%20vital%20for%20preserving%20biodiversity%20and%20ensuring%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367156%2Fmanipur-pangolin-conservation-wildlife-trust-india-community-efforts-ecosystem-villages%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Foodies%20Share%207%