ree%20years.%20The%20reasons%20they%20cite%20are%20a%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20need%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccomplicated%20procedures%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-5-1726670615.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20her%20work%20Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20has%20ensured%20over%20a%20million%20poor%20people%20have%20secured%20employment%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-5-1726670615.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-5-1726670615-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-5-1726670615-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-5-1726670615-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-5-1726670615-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366613%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20her%20work%20Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20has%20ensured%20over%20a%20million%20women%20have%20secured%20employment%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Hand%20in%20Hand%20India%20steps%20in.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20loans%20to%20members%20of%20our%20self-help%20groups%20through%20MFIs%20or%20banks%20to%20help%20their%20businesses%20take%20off.%20The%20increase%20in%20livelihood%20activities%20also%20ensures%20that%20women%20are%20able%20to%20repay%20their%20loans%20with%20no%20trouble%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Sankar.%20She%20adds%20that%20through%20the%20%E2%80%98Graduated%20Entrepreneurs%20Programme%E2%80%99%2C